---
title: HelloHero: Smokey Pork & Creamy Slaw with Sesame Carrot Fries & Garlic Aioli
description: Give pork loin a dash of flair with smokey All-American spice blend for a melody of robust flavours. Don’t stop there! Ramp up your dish with a creamy slaw tossed around with cucumber. All you need now are some sesame-speckled veggie fries and a sauce to dip them in.

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving and under 40g carbohydrates per serving.*
